Module io.helidon.integrations.vault
Package io.helidon.integrations.vault

Interface SecretsRx

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CubbyholeSecretsRx, DbSecretsRx, Kv1SecretsRx, Kv2SecretsRx, PkiSecretsRx, TransitSecretsRx
    public interface SecretsRx
    All engines provide an implementation of this interface with specific methods for these engines. This is a reactive base for secrets.
